OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FWords by Emily Youlton, Senior
OL,7,FPolitics Producer
OL,9,FAndy Burnham promised to "make
OL,10,Fpolitics work, to make it work better"
OL,11,Fin his first speech as prime minister
OL,12,Fon Downing Street.
OL,14,FThe speech marked the start of his
OL,15,Fpremiership as he headed through that
OL,16,Ffamous black door and promised to get
OL,17,Fstarted on giving "people some
OL,18,Fbreathing space now".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FAfter a busy first day appointing his
OL,7,Fcabinet, day two turned straight to
OL,8,Fhis first policy announcement of
OL,9,Fcutting VAT on electricity bills from
OL,10,F5% to 0% in October.
OL,12,FWith no real manifesto yet, there are
OL,13,Flots of unknowns relating to Burnham's
OL,14,Fplans and policies, and there will be
OL,15,Fsome challenges for the new PM that
OL,16,Fmay not be on the top of his list.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FBut as he made clear to his cabinet at
OL,7,Ftheir first meeting on Tuesday: "We
OL,8,Fneed to be a cost of living
OL,9,Fgovernment" and give people a "sense
OL,10,Fthat help is coming".
OL,12,FHere, ITV News looks at some key
OL,13,Fpolicies that Burnham will prioritise
OL,14,Fin his premiership.
OL,16,FCost of Living
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FBurnham has said that his team will be
OL,7,F"a cost of living government" and has
OL,8,Fsaid that he will set out his full
OL,9,Fplan to tackle the crisis in the
OL,10,Fcoming days.
OL,12,FHis first policy announcement to cut
OL,13,FVAT from electricity bills is
OL,14,Festimated to save the average
OL,15,Fhousehold around #45 a year, less than
OL,16,F#4 a month.
OL,18,FConsumer expert Martin Lewis also
OL,19,Findicated that with the energy price
OL,20,Fcap set to rise in October, this
OL,21,Fsaving will feel even smaller.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FThe cut will be funded by scrapping
OL,7,Fthe previous government's digital ID
OL,8,Fprogramme, although former cabinet
OL,9,Fminister Darren Jones said on social
OL,10,Fmedia that the project was unfunded.
OL,12,FTime is not on any government's side
OL,13,Fand Burnham knows he must act quickly
OL,14,Fto make an impact on people's lives,
OL,15,Fwith new polling of voters from
OL,16,FDeltapoll showing Labour level with
OL,17,FReform at 28%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
