OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FIt is thought Burnham wants to bring
OL,7,Fback the #2 bus cap, if he has the
OL,8,Ffunds to do so, after Starmer's
OL,9,Fgovernment raised it to #3 for single
OL,10,Fjourneys in January 2025.
OL,12,FThis builds on his transport policy as
OL,13,FMayor of Greater Manchester, where
OL,14,Flocal fares on the Bee Network were
OL,15,Fcapped at #2.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FIt is understood transport secretary
OL,7,FHeidi Alexander is on board with this
OL,8,Fidea and lobbied the government to
OL,9,Finclude free bus travel or five to 15
OL,10,Fyear olds as part of the Great British
OL,11,FSummer Savings scheme.
OL,13,FOther rumoured cost of living policy
OL,14,Fideas include rent freezes and
OL,15,Fincreasing the tax threshold on
OL,16,Fpersonal allowance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
