OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FBurnham also has ambitious plans for
OL,7,Fthe "biggest council housebuilding
OL,8,Fprogramme since the post-war period"
OL,9,Fand will hope the return of Angela
OL,10,FRayner as housing secretary will help
OL,11,Fhim achieve this.
OL,13,FSarah Elliot, CEO of Shelter welcomed
OL,14,FBurnham's plans and said: "The prime
OL,15,Fminister has given Angela Rayner a
OL,16,Fclear mandate to roll out a council
OL,17,Fhousing revolution and put an end to
OL,18,Frough sleeping ` now it's her time to
OL,19,Fdeliver.
OL,26,@vD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
