PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,F"Having grown up in social housing,
OL,7,FRayner knows better than anyone that
OL,8,Fan affordable, decent home is the
OL,9,Ffoundation for everything, giving
OL,10,Fpeople the building blocks they need
OL,11,Fto get on in life and setting children
OL,12,Fup to thrive."
OL,14,FDuring his essentially non-existent
OL,15,Fcampaign to become Labour leader,
OL,16,FBurnham set out a plan to create a
OL,17,FNumber 10 of the North, tasked with
OL,18,Frolling out "good growth in every
OL,19,Fpostcode".
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
