SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FThis shift to relocate large parts of
OL,7,Fthe Whitehall machine to Manchester
OL,8,Fhas already begun, with Downing Street
OL,9,Fconfirming that civil servants are
OL,10,Falready working at the new northern
OL,11,Fbase ` an existing government building
OL,12,Fand claim it will not cost no extra
OL,13,Fmoney.
OL,15,FBurnham, a Manchester resident, is
OL,16,Fkeen to make the most of the base for
OL,17,Fhimself, and according to his
OL,18,Fspokesperson, he expects to work out
OL,19,Fof No 10 North "at least one day a
OL,20,Fweek" where his diary allows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FThe promise of improving "every
OL,7,Fpostcode" is ambitious and Burnham is
OL,8,Fat risk of alienating rural and
OL,9,Fsouthern communities and MPs, who
OL,10,Fdon't know much about the 'King of the
OL,11,FNorth' or feel he understands their
OL,12,Fissues.
OL,14,FLabour MP for South West Norfolk,
OL,15,FTerry Jermy told ITV News, that
OL,16,FBurnham needs to understand that
OL,17,F"rural areas are different to your
OL,18,FManchesters and your Londons of the
OL,19,Fworld".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
