SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FForeign policy hasn't been much at the
OL,7,Fforefront of Burnham's run for the top
OL,8,Fjob but in his speech outside No 10,
OL,9,FBurnham promised to "honour
OL,10,Fcommitments on defence to our
OL,11,Finternational partners".
OL,13,FIn an unexpected move, Burnham
OL,14,Fappointed former defence secretary
OL,15,FJohn Healey as his chancellor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FHealey quit Starmer's cabinet
OL,7,Ffollowing a row over funding for the
OL,8,Fdefence investment plan (Dip) but now
OL,9,Fhe will be responsible for delivering
OL,10,Fthat investment, questions are raised
OL,11,Fas to whether defence will get more.
OL,13,FIn one of his last acts as PM, Starmer
OL,14,Freleased the investment plan last
OL,15,Fmonth with an increase in funding of
OL,16,F#15 billion top of current defence
OL,17,Fspending, but left Burnham and now
OL,18,FHealey with a #4.7 billion black hole
OL,19,Fto fill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FQuestioned about defence spending on
OL,7,FTuesday, new defence secretary Wes
OL,8,FStreeting said: "I'm absolutely
OL,9,Fdelighted that my friend and
OL,10,Fpredecessor John Healey has taken on
OL,11,Fthe challenge of Chancellor of the
OL,12,FExchequer and his position on defence
OL,13,Finvestment is on the record, as is
OL,14,Fmine."
