OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FRe-industrialisation and public
OL,7,Fownership
OL,9,FBurnham has consistently said he wants
OL,10,Fto re-industrialise Britain and
OL,11,Frepeated these calls on the steps of
OL,12,FNo 10 on Monday.
OL,14,FHe has spoken extensively about
OL,15,Fwanting to improve technical education
OL,16,Ffor young people as part of this
OL,17,Fstrategy as well as tackling the youth
OL,18,Funemployment crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31319
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FSitting in the soft left of politics,
OL,7,FBurnham is also keen on public
OL,8,Fownership of energy and transport,
OL,9,Fagain reflecting his work on the Bee
OL,10,Ftransport network in Manchester.
OL,12,FUnder Starmer's leadership, the
OL,13,Frenationalisation of railways began,
OL,14,Fwith the transport secretary, who has
OL,15,Fremained in post overseeing the launch
OL,16,Fof Great British Rail.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31320
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784702922
OL,3,CWhat's first on Andy Burnham's agenda
OL,4,Cas prime minister?
OL,6,FBurnham will also face a challenge
OL,7,Fearly on with Thames Water reaching
OL,8,Fbreaking point, and proposals for the
OL,9,Fgovernment to take golden shares,
OL,10,Fsimilar to that of Royal Mail.
OL,12,FWhile campaigning to return to
OL,13,FWestminster as Makerfield MP, Burnham
OL,14,Fsaid there was "a very strong case for
OL,15,Fpublic ownership" to resolve Thames
OL,16,FWater's problems.
OL,18,FNew environment secretary Dame Angela
OL,19,FEagle will have to get stuck in with
OL,20,Fthe water board very quickly.
OL,26,@vD@POUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/21
